# MIYAR 2.0 — Intelligent Intake System

> **Goal:** Replace the 50-field manual form with a multimodal AI intake — drop files, paste URLs, or describe your project. MIYAR translates everything into structured [ProjectInputs](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/shared/miyar-types.ts#36-102). The form becomes a review checkpoint, not a data entry burden.

---

## Codebase Audit Results

The original plan flagged 5 "must build" gaps. **3 of 5 already exist:**

| Component | Original Status | Actual Status |
|-----------|----------------|---------------|
| S3 upload infrastructure | ❌ Missing | ✅ [storage.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/storage.ts) — [storagePut()](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/storage.ts#42-81), [storageGet()](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/storage.ts#82-99), presigned URLs |
| `project_assets` table | ❌ Missing | ✅ [schema.ts:595](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/drizzle/schema.ts#L595-L627) — 13 columns, 12 categories |
| Multimodal LLM | ✅ Ready | ✅ [llm.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/_core/llm.ts) — `image_url`, `file_url` (PDF, audio, video) |
| Floor plan analyzer | ✅ Ready | ✅ [floor-plan-analyzer.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/design/floor-plan-analyzer.ts) — [analyzeFloorPlan()](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/design/floor-plan-analyzer.ts#89-198) |
| AI Intake Engine | ❌ Must build | ❌ Must build |

**What's truly new:** AI Intake Engine, Intake Router, NewProject UI, AI Assist buttons.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Schema extension needed.** The existing `project_assets` table lacks `aiExtractionResult` and `aiContributions` columns. We'll add 2 columns via ALTER TABLE. No data loss, no migration risk.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Voice input scope.** Browser `MediaRecorder` → Gemini audio/mp4 is trivial. Recommend including it in Phase 2.0-A as a P0 since it's ~20 lines of code on top of the existing `file_url` support. Agree?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Chat refinement (`refineWithChat`) scope.** This is the most complex feature. Recommend deferring to Phase 2.0-F (fast follow) and shipping the core upload → auto-fill → review flow first. Agree?

---

## Build Sequence

### Phase 2.0-A: Schema Extension + Upload Endpoint (~30 min)

#### [MODIFY] [schema.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/drizzle/schema.ts)
- Add `aiExtractionResult` (JSON) and `aiContributions` (JSON) columns to `project_assets`
- Add `assetType` enum column: `image`, [pdf](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/docs/miyar-assets.s3.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com_reports_4_design_brief-3NdcfMJN.html_X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=AKIA5WPGPNOICU4GX7OZ%252F20260225%252Feu-north-1%252Fs3%252Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260225T.pdf), `audio`, `video`, `url`, `text_note`

#### [NEW] `server/routers/intake.ts`
- `getUploadUrl` — generates presigned S3 upload URL using existing [storagePut()](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/storage.ts#42-81)
- `uploadAsset` — stores asset record in `project_assets` after client uploads to S3

---

### Phase 2.0-B: AI Intake Engine (~2 hours)

#### [NEW] `server/engines/intake/ai-intake-engine.ts`
Core function: `processIntakeAssets(assets[], existingInputs?) → IntakeResult`

- Calls `invokeLLM` with multimodal content (images + PDFs + text)
- Uses `outputSchema` to force typed JSON matching `Partial<ProjectInputs>`
- Reuses [analyzeFloorPlan()](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/design/floor-plan-analyzer.ts#89-198) from [floor-plan-analyzer.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/design/floor-plan-analyzer.ts) when floor plans detected
- Returns per-field `confidence` (high/medium/low) and `reasoning`

```typescript
interface IntakeResult {
  suggestedInputs: Partial<ProjectInputs>;
  confidence: Record<string, 'high' | 'medium' | 'low'>;
  reasoning: Record<string, string>;
  extractedInsights: { detectedStyle, detectedMaterials, detectedTier, ... };
  warnings: string[];
}
```

#### [NEW] `server/engines/intake/url-scraper.ts`
- Fetches URL content → Gemini extracts supplier info, material tiers, pricing signals
- Reuses crawler patterns from [crawler.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/ingestion/crawler.ts)

#### [NEW] `server/engines/intake/ai-intake-engine.test.ts`
- Unit tests for intake processing with mock assets
- Test per-field confidence mapping
- Test floor plan detection and delegation
- Test URL scraping extraction

---

### Phase 2.0-C: Intake Router (Full) (~1 hour)

#### [MODIFY] `server/routers/intake.ts`
- `processAssets` — accepts assets array, stores in DB, calls AI engine, returns `IntakeResult`
- `applyIntakeSuggestions` — merges AI suggestions into project draft
- Register in [routers.ts](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/routers.ts)

---

### Phase 2.0-D: NewProject Rewrite (~3 hours)

#### [MODIFY] [NewProject.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/pages/NewProject.tsx) — full UI rewrite
**Default view: "Talk to MIYAR"**
- Drag-and-drop upload zone (images, PDFs, audio, video)
- URL paste input (supplier/competitor sites)
- Free-text description box ("50 luxury apartments in Dubai Marina, Japandi...")
- Voice recorder using browser `MediaRecorder` API
- "Analyze & Auto-Fill ✨" button → calls `intake.processAssets`
- After AI processes → transitions to existing [ProjectForm.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/components/ProjectForm.tsx) with fields pre-filled
- "Skip to Manual Form →" bypass link

**Pre-filled form enhancements:**
- Green badges on high-confidence AI-populated fields
- Yellow badges on medium-confidence fields needing review
- "Why this value?" tooltip per field showing AI reasoning
- Asset thumbnails in sidebar panel

---

### Phase 2.0-E: AI Assist on Existing Form (~1 hour)

#### [MODIFY] [ProjectForm.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/components/ProjectForm.tsx)
- Add small "✨ AI Assist" button per section
- Button calls `intake.processAssets` with uploaded assets scoped to that section
- Suggests values for that section based on already-entered data

---

### Phase 2.0-F: Fast Follow (defer)
- `refineWithChat` — conversational refinement of suggestions
- Asset gallery on [ProjectDetail.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/pages/ProjectDetail.tsx)

