## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
```bash
# Run AI Intake Engine unit tests
npx vitest run server/engines/intake/ai-intake-engine.test.ts

# Full regression suite
npx vitest run
```

### Manual Verification
1. Navigate to `http://localhost:3000/projects/new`
2. Verify "Talk to MIYAR" canvas appears with upload zone and text area
3. Upload a mood board image → verify AI extracts style, tier, material suggestions
4. Upload a floor plan PDF → verify [analyzeFloorPlan()](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/server/engines/design/floor-plan-analyzer.ts#89-198) runs and populates room data
5. Paste a supplier URL → verify material/pricing extraction
6. Type a project description → verify AI fills relevant fields
7. Click "Analyze & Auto-Fill" → verify form transitions with green/yellow confidence badges
8. Verify "Skip to Manual Form" still works (existing flow unchanged)
9. Complete project creation → verify all engines receive valid [ProjectInputs](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/shared/miyar-types.ts#36-102)
